{"tid":1359233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好撚再講咩唔記得五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-24T05:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:52:47.000Z","uid":32954,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8260731b680ec29110a50fec939f930daeb0ae59","tid":1359233,"uid":32954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"邊有人唔記得？係咪唔係每秒提住就等於冇提？<br />\n<br />\n去元朗又話人唔記得，整連儂牆又話唔記得，光復屯門又話唔記得。<br />\n<br />\n有份出嚟嘅人係唔會唔記得五大訴求，但我地心底裡唔知唔撚會有回應咩？唔係唔提訴求，而係一路做其他戰線，一路都要繼續爭取。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：次次發夢都係前線<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"6553efe66c779a2a23557d6aacf39782a7af492d","tid":1359233,"uid":170051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最緊要守住運動三原則 對準政權 各有各做<br />\n<br />\n［重要］點解仲有人支持政府？一定要睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354482</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89a8426b77710c0a802726fc25331dec345e65d0","tid":1359233,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n要政府改革應該冇用 , 只有革命先有用!"},{"pid":"107cafb5eaff3e41e3887b3036e96a32b2a23924","tid":1359233,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}